snippet.title: A Midlevel Dog v1.1.0, with both endings
snippet.description:
A playthrough of A Midlevel Dog, v1.1.0, with both endings. The "good" ending begins at 8:56. You can play the game here for free: https://andyman404.itch.io/midleveldog
